identify　　vt.1. 确认;识别;鉴定,验明[(+as)]She identified him as her attacker.她认出他就是袭击她的人。I cannot identify this signature.我识别不出这是谁的签字。
2. 视...(与...)为同一事物[(+with)]
Never identify wealth with happiness.
千万不要把财富和幸福等同起来。
3. 使参与;使合作[(+with)]；支持
The politician refused to identify himself with the Administration's foreign policy.
那位政治家拒不支持政府的外交政策。
